  ],
  "remarks": "Deputy of the “Luhansk Economic Union” in the “National Council” of the “Luhansk People’s Republic”. Stood as a candidate in the so-called “elections” of 2 November 2014 to the post of so-called “Head” of the “Luhansk People’s Republic”. Those “elections” were in breach of Ukrainian law and therefore illegal. Former “Head” of the so-called “Federation of Trade Unions”. Member of the so-called “People’s Council” of the “Luhansk People’s Republic”. Current Chairman of the Board of the Interregional Public Organisation “Union of Luhansk Communities”, representative of the Integration Committee “Russia-Donbas”.",
